"Disk /gnu/store/yhylv1bp5b2ypb97pd3bbhz6jk5nbhxw-disk-image: 1714MB\n"
"Sector size (logical/physical): 512B/512B\n"
"Partition Table: msdos\n"
"Disk Flags:\n"
"\n"
