"Number  Start   End     Size    Type     File system  Flags\n"
" 1      1049kB  43.0MB  41.9MB  primary  fat16        esp\n"
" 2      43.0MB  95.4MB  52.4MB  primary  ext4\n"
" 3      95.4MB  1714MB  1619MB  primary  ext4         boot\n"
msgstr ""
