"(use-modules (gnu system images pine64))\n"
"(operating-system\n"
"  (inherit pine64-barebones-os)\n"
"  (timezone \"Europe/Athens\"))\n"
msgstr ""
"(use-modules (gnu system images pine64))\n"
"(operating-system\n"
"  (inherit pine64-barebones-os)\n"
"  (timezone \"Europe/Athens\"))\n"

msgid "to customize the @code{pine64-barebones-os}, and run:"
